- 'Recent technical analysis' refers to analyses conducted on or after January 1, 2022;
- 'Buy' indicates a positive recommendation based on technical analysis.

- "top 10% of the most profitable trades" refers to the highest 10% of trades ranked by profit_loss within each instrument_id;
